  "notes": "This pressing has the etching \"-◁\" in the run-outs, indication of pressing at [l=Capitol Records Pressing Plant, Winchester].\n(Copies with \"IAM\" (in a triangle) are pressed at Capitol Records Pressing Plant, Scranton)\n(Copies with \"0\" pressed at Capitol Records Pressing Plant, Jacksonville, Illinois)\n\nFirst press identifier - Maggie Mae credited to \"P.D.\" (this pressing)\n(Second Pressing credited to \"P.D. arr. Lennon, McCartney, Harrison, Starkey\")\n\nRed Apple label with 'MFD. BY APPLE RECORDS, INC.' in red ink on bottom of Side A.\n\nThanks to George Martin / Glyn Johns / Billy Preston / Harold Seider / Mal Davies / Peter Bown / Richard Hewson / Brian Rogers.\nRecorded in England.\n\nRunouts etched; Bell Sound stamped\n'17,500-xx'; '17,501-yy' may display 3 hand etched dots below the xx and yy.",
